            <h3>By pressing "Accept" you are accepting the following Terms and Conditions</h3>
<h4>I. Area of application</h4>
<p>The terms and conditions contained in this document will apply to the relationship between the visitor (hereinafter referred to as "Client") and Pet Hotel from the moment the reservation is requested until the date the period of accommodation at the hotel ends.</p>
<p>Where the Terms and Conditions do not refer, the law in force will apply.</p>
<h4>II. Conclusion of the contract</h4>
<p>1. When requesting a room reservation, the Client makes an accommodation proposal to Pet Hotel. If rooms are available, Pet Hotel will provide the Client with a reservation code.</p>
<p>2. The Client is informed that room reservations in Pet Hotel hotels made by third parties (tour operators or room reservation portals on the internet) imply the issuance of a reservation code other than the one issued directly by Pet Hotel, although it is equally valid.</p>
<p>3. Room reservation requests made directly to Pet Hotel or through third parties are not binding and do not oblige Pet Hotel to enter into a contract with the Client. Pet Hotel always has the right to refuse to enter into a contract and provide a room at its sole discretion.</p>
<p>4. Pet Hotel only guarantees the Client the availability of a room in the reserved category and not the provision of a specific hotel room.</p>
<h4>III. Type of reservations and their cancellation</h4>
<p>1. In Pet Hotel hotels, the Client may make two types of reservations, "simple" reservations and "guaranteed" reservations.</p>
<p>2. The Simple Reservation is the reservation of a room in a hotPet Hotel in which the Client does not need to make any prior payment or provide a means of payment.</p>
<p>3. The Guaranteed Reservation is the reservation of a room in a hotPet Hotel in which there is the supply, by the Client, of the valid and complete data of a credit card, or the reservation accompanied by the sending of a proof of transfer bank of the entire value of the reserved accommodation.</p>
<p>4. The Simple Reservation can be freely canceled by the Client, without any cost, until 4:00 p.m. on the day of the reservation.</p>
<p>5. The Simple Reservation will expire automatically if the Client does not show up at the hotel until 4:00 p.m. on the day of the reservation, in which case Pet Hotel can immediately provide the reserved room to any other Client without the Client who made the reservation being able to claim any compensation from Pet Hotel for any title whatsoever.</p>
<p>6. The Guaranteed Reservation may be freely canceled by the Client until 4 pm on the day of the reservation, at no cost, without prejudice to the specific conditions for the periods of fairs and special events provided in section XVIII.</p>
<p>7. If the Guaranteed Reservation is canceled in accordance with the previous number and the Client has already made the payment of the value - in the terms of the provisions of the final part of number 3 of this clause - Pet Hotel will restore the values paid.</p>
<p>8. In the event that the request for cancellation of the guaranteed reservation is made after 4 pm, the Client will be charged the value of the room for that day, leaving the reservation without effect on the day immediately to follow. The same principle applies if the Client does not show up on the day of the Reservation without having the reservation he made canceled in due time.</p>
<h4>IV. Arrival and departure</h4>
<p>1. Pet Hotel will provide the Client with a room of the category reserved from the date of arrival or, if the Client has not made the reservation and hires the accommodation at the hotel reception, depending on the category intended and in accordance with the availability of the hotel, starting at 2:00 p.m. and no later than 5:00 p.m. on the day of entry into the hotel.</p>
<p>2. Upon arrival at the hotel, the Client must immediately precede the payment of the value of the room, the number of nights of stay and additional services.</p>
<p>3. Against the total payment of the value Pet Hotel will provide the Client with an access code to the room that will be valid during the contracted period of stay.</p>
<p>4. On the departure date the Client will have to leave the room unoccupied of people and goods and without any damage until 12 noon.</p>
<p>5. In the event that the room is not left until 12 noon on the day of departure, compensation corresponding to the value of a one-night stay at the hotel will be charged immediately, with only the right to use the room in that period if the hotel has room availability. Otherwise he will have to pay the compensation and leave the room as soon as possible.</p>
<h4>V. Animals</h4>
<p>1. The accommodation of animals in the Pet Hotel hotels is expressly obliged.</p>
<h4>VI. Terms of use</h4>
<p>1. Only the people indicated in the accommodation reservation will have the right to use the hotel room.</p>
<p>2. Clients should treat the hotel room with care and consideration.</p>
<p>3. The Client must treat the other clients of the hotel with consideration and respect the hotel rules posted in the same and, where appropriate, which are also part of the accommodation contract.</p>
<p>4. The Client is not allowed to cook food brought, either in the hotel room or in any other place of the hotel facilities.</p>
<p>5. Children under the age of 14 must be supervised by an adult Client at all times during their stay at the hotel.</p>
<p>6. The Client is strongly advised not to keep or leave without any money, jewelry, valuables or other valuable items left in the hotel room or in vehicles parked at Pet Hotel.</p>
<p>7. Pet Hotel offers its Clients a central hotel safe in which they can store valuables, provided that they are duly identified in a document for this purpose.</p>
<p>8. Pet Hotel does not assume any responsibility in the event of theft, loss or deterioration of valuables such as money, jewelery or other objects of considerable value if such events take place in the hotel room or inside parked vehicles. in the parking lot.</p>
<h4>VII. Access to the hotel room by Pet Hotel</h4>
<p>Pet Hotel and its staff have the right to enter the hotel room, during the Client's stay, in order to carry out cleaning, repair and similar work. </p>
<h4>VIII. Value of the stay and other prices</h4>
<p>1. The value of the stay to be paid by the Client constitutes the compensation for the availability of the use of the hotel room, in the period from arrival to departure.</p>
<p>2. The total price of the stay will be charged per night, regardless of whether the Client has actually used the room or has spent the night there.</p>
<p>3. The applicable rates are the agreed prices or the price indicated in the Pet Hotel price list in force on the date the contract is signed. Pet Hotel will have the right to increase or decrease the values if a period of more than four months elapses between the reservation date by the Client and the arrival date or if any tax, visitor contribution or other orders are changed or introduced.</p>
<p>4. VAT is added to the rates or values indicated in the terms and in the accommodation contract, unless expressly stated otherwise.</p>
<h4>IX. Payment terms</h4>
<p>1. The value of the stay and the prices of additional services must be paid in advance, at the time the Client arrives at the hotel, regardless of the billing date.</p>
<p>2. If the duration of the Client's stay is not detailed, the price of the stay and the values of the additional services for each night must be paid until 12 noon.</p>
<p>3. In the case of stays without a detailed departure date, the non-payment of the price of the stay and additional services in the terms established in the previous number determines the immediate termination of the contract and the Client is immediately obliged to leave the room and deliver it to Pet Hotel without people or property and in good condition.</p>
<p>4. The fees for additional services, in the meaning of number 1 will be, for example, amounts related to parking or breakfast prices, and other amounts that are not expressly mentioned in the accommodation contract, which are part of the value of the stay.</p>
<p>5. Pet Hotel accepts payment in euros, transfers, CE Maestro, Visa Electron and credit cards: Visa and MasterCard. Other means of payment are only allowed in exceptional cases, with the consent sometimes given by Pet Hotel.</p>
<h4>X. Claims for material defects</h4>
<p>1. The Client must inspect the hotel room upon arrival and immediately report any defects that he may find at the hotel reception.</p>
<p>2. Any defect that appears during the stay must be communicated at the hotel reception so that the Client is aware of it.</p>
<p>3. In the event that it is verified that there is indeed a defect in the Client's room, Pet Hotel has the right to choose between repairing and relocating the Client in a room that has at least the same category contracted with the Client.</p>
<p>4. For the aforementioned purposes, only serious defects capable of jeopardizing the level of service and quality of Pet Hotel are considered, and Pet Hotel is not obliged to take measures in the case of irrelevant, unreasonable or having complaints. to do with details that do not conflict with the minimum level of service contracted.</p>
<p>5. In the event that Pet Hotel does not have the necessary means to repair the relevant defect or to replace the Client's room with another of a similar or higher category, the Client may only terminate the contract and receive the amount paid for the room. , not being able to demand anything more from Pet Hotel by whatever title. </p>
