<p>2. Pet Hotel does not assume any responsibility for loss of data provided by the Client in the case of electronic transmission of payment data, being only responsible if there is a culpable action.</p>
<p>3. Pet Hotel does not assume any responsibility for damages or accidents that occur inside the room or any other part of the hotel, except if these accidents are caused by the fault of Pet Hotel.</p>
<p>4. Pet Hotel will not be held responsible to the Client in case of delay in room availability, even if there are valid reasons for the timely non-availability of the room.</p>
<p>5. For the purposes of the previous number, valid reasons will be considered for the impossibility or more difficult availability of a room, for example, strikes, blockades, natural disasters, accidents in the room or in the hotel.</p>
<p>6. In the event of a delay in room availability beyond 4 pm on the day of the reservation, the Client may freely terminate the contract without having the right to demand any compensation from Pet Hotel for any title whatsoever.</p>
<p>7. Pet Hotel does not assume any responsibility for acts carried out by any hotel worker, unless he is in his normal working period, duly identified and uniformed like any other worker in the company.</p>
