<p>1. The terms and conditions fully regulate the Client's stay at the hotel and their use of the room.</p>
<p>2. No verbal agreement is reached in the accommodation contract and all alterations to the contract between the parties will necessarily have to be in the written document and signed by both, except in the case of a unilateral declaration, in which case they must be included in the document. writing signed by the issuer.</p>
<p>3. Pet Hotel will have the right to have third parties to fulfill their obligations under and within the scope of the accommodation contract.</p>
<p>4. The invalidity of one or more of the previous provisions does not affect the validity of the other provisions. The invalid provision will be replaced by the valid provision, the closest to the commercial and legal intentions of the parties or, if this is not possible, by the legislation in force. </p>
